sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant M as Mobile App
    participant B as Backend API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant AI as Mock AI Gateway (malformed)

    U->>M: Open lesson
    M->>B: POST /lesson-sessions
    B->>DB: INSERT lesson_session
    B-->>M: SessionResponse

    U->>M: Submit narrative text
    M->>B: POST /lesson-sessions/{id}/submissions
    B->>DB: INSERT submission
    B-->>M: SubmitTextResponse

    M->>B: POST /lesson-sessions/{id}/process
    B->>DB: SELECT submission
    B->>AI: analyze_submission()

    Note over AI: MOCK_AI_FIXTURE_MODE=malformed
    AI-->>B: Malformed analysis result

    B->>B: schema_valid = false
    B->>DB: UPDATE session → FAILED
    B->>DB: INSERT audit_event (failure)
    B-->>M: ProcessResponse (status: FAILED)

    M->>M: Show safe error state
    Note over M: No lesson completion<br/>No mastery evidence<br/>No policy decision

    alt Pedagogical validation failure
        B->>B: pedagogical → passed: false
        B->>DB: INSERT validation_result (pedagogical:FAILED)
        B->>DB: UPDATE session → REJECTED
        B-->>M: ProcessResponse (status: REJECTED)
    end

    alt Linguistic validation failure
        B->>B: linguistic → passed: false
        B->>DB: INSERT validation_result (linguistic:FAILED)
        B->>DB: UPDATE session → REJECTED
        B-->>M: ProcessResponse (status: REJECTED)
    end
